I've analyzed your component. The issue is that you're rendering a list without proper key props. Here's the fix:

```jsx
function ItemList({ items }) {
  return (
    <ul>
      {items.map((item) => (
        <li key={item.id}>{item.name}</li>
      ))}
    </ul>
  );
}
```

Always use unique keys when rendering lists in React.
